es.utils.mapper.impl.object

Class DirectMapper<T,U>

  • java.lang.Object
    • es.utils.mapper.impl.MapperObject<T,U>
      • es.utils.mapper.impl.object.DirectMapper<T,U>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the origin object
    U - the type of the destination object
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractConverter

    public class DirectMapper<T,U>
extends MapperObject<T,U>
    This class customize the abstract class MapperObject creating a MapperObject that convert on object of type T into a U with a custom conversion function.
    Author:
    eschoysman
